comments: Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Jackson (LAC) as he loses his balance in transition.
Holmes (SAC) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Jackson (LAC).
Holmes (SAC) moves forward into Morris Sr. (LAC) and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
George (LAC) makes contact to Davis's (SAC) arm that affects his control of the ball.
Holmes (SAC) legally contests the jump shot attempt by George (LAC).
Morris Sr. (LAC) reaches in and makes contact to Holmes (SAC) that affects his SQBR.
Mitchell (SAC) backs into Zubac (LAC) and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Zubac (LAC) makes marginal contact with Haliburton (SAC) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) gets his hand on the ball and then Zubac (LAC) cleanly blocks Holmes' (SAC) shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) makes contact to Jackson's (LAC) arm that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Morris Sr. (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge is successful.  Morris Sr. makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) during the rebounding sequence.
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Morris Sr. (LAC) extends his leg into Hield (SAC) and creates the marginal contact during his jump shot attempt.
